{
  "stem": "20142.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Jewish community center was on Grzybowska street, spelled G-R-Z-Y-S-- Y-B-O-- B-O-W-S-K-A.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In-- and the man in charge of Jewish community was Dr.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[POLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Once you got the ID, you had to expect the Germans would send you some notification to report to certain places of work.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were possibility that people did not have to go to work if they could know how to pay for it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was something like working talons-- talons, spelled T-A-L-O-N.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Like a booklet of tickets that you had to surrender to the group of-- of the foremen at such place of work.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was mostly military outposts in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Like on the airport, you have no [INAUDIBLE] or-- or the damaged building that they wanted to convert for their own use.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was too young for-- at that time to get any talons.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I remember on several occasion, I want work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My members of my family could not go to such work, I took their talons to go to work for them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First time I got to work, there was some infantry place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "U-J-A-Z-D-- D-O-W-S-K, in Warsaw, clearing out debris from bombardments of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We're living with part of our family, mother's family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Majority of mother's family is from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were some 56 members that I know of.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With the sister of my-- my mother and Dzika, the street, spelled D-Z-I-K-A.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Dzika in Polish means wild street.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My aunt was Rose Medzycki, spelled M-E-D-Z-Y-C-K-I.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Medzycki.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were receiving at the beginning a very nice one.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we find that we're all in quarters renting a place from some people in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In the District of Jewish quarters, and this was on [NON-ENGLISH] street in Warsaw, off Zamenhof Street.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Four.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
